criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. age ≥18 years old;

          2. KPS≥60；

          3. Radiation enteritis diagnosed by colonoscopy after finishing radiotherapy；

          4. Grade1 to 3 toxicity based on RTOG/EORTC：

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Pregnant or breast-feeding women;

          2. Complicated with other severe disease, including relapsing cancers, organ failure,
             heart diseases;

          3. Lifespan less than 3 months.
